_sText:
You are somehow catched into the dark. Long long away from planet. You are waking up with your squad. You cant see, you need to use flashlight. Everything is dark, blood everywhere. Hostages got killed. Terrorists wants too bomb them. Save the dead bodies from getting blown up.

Be an assassin and go in stealth mode.
Get behind an enemy and kill it, no noise.
1 shot 1 kill.
Jump from roof and scare your enemies.

Enjoy
This map contains blood.

Map creator is myself
Xgjengen
